data.description: Welcome to this stunning, nearly new home, a rare gem that's only been lived in for a few months. Life’s unexpected turns present an unparalleled opportunity for you to become the proud owner of this beautiful home located within minutes of Bennington High.  Boasting an impressive layout spread across two levels, this home features 5 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 modern bathrooms, catering comfortably to both large families and those who love to entertain. The heart of the home is its open-plan living area, where natural light streams through large windows, illuminating the space with a warm, welcoming glow.  For those who appreciate convenience and style, this home comes with a unique offer: all furniture is open to remain, should you choose. Don’t miss out on this chance!  Schedule your viewing today and step into your future home, where new memories await.
